# Continuous Integration (CI)

This folder contains configuration files for automated testing and validation.

## Planned CI steps:
- **Linting:** check JSON course templates and code style.
- **Schema validation:** verify generated course data follows the defined schema.
- **SCORM/xAPI tests:** automatically generate and validate sample packages.
- **License check:** ensure all media files include proper attribution (CC0/CC BY).
- **Accessibility audit:** run AXE on representative screens (target â‰¥ 95% WCAG 2.1 AA).

Once the project reaches M2, full CI workflows will be enabled.
